{"tid":178409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會辯最低工資　張宇人洗碗難申公屋論惹火","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T16:20:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52fd7f03b281e222d90551b455ee54c0aaab6b6d","tid":178409,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/photo/bkn-20170329155744315-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170329191708\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170329155744315-0329_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170329191708&h=213c9bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會大會下午就《2017年最低工資條例(修訂附表3)公告》、即把最低工資由32.5港元增加至34.5港元進行辯論。勞工界立法會議員陸頌雄表示，現行最低工資水平未能保障打工仔，不論多努力，生活仍捉襟見肘，難以養家。惟飲食界議員張宇人指，最低工資帶來漣漪效應，令飲食業於各薪酬階梯都面臨加薪壓力，更指洗碗工人普遍月薪1.6萬至1.7萬港元，一個家庭兩個洗碗就「公屋都上唔到」，批評最低工資是政府錯誤決定、各政黨為爭取市民支持的「糖衣毒藥」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，張宇人的言論隨即惹來其他議員批評。議員劉小麗揶揄「有最低工資就有張宇人」，又批評現行最低工資制度做到「天一半地一半」，政府「又要威又要戴頭盔」，最低工資水平僅夠工人「吊命」，張宇人「呢啲大老闆」就一直作出恐嚇，認為政府不應再卸膊，應如爭取高官加薪一樣，為市民爭取權益。<br />\n<br />\n議員梁耀忠則稱，中國人傳統是過年前出「雙糧」，過完年加人工，惟最低工資「兩年一檢」，非年年加人工，已是違反傳統，希望政府可對「兩年一檢」作出修訂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329155744315-0329_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170329%2Fbkn-20170329155744315-0329_00822_001.html&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=38880941\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170329/bkn-20170329155744315-0329_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"77da4ad5551718de9920d1a9a309557ce8fd8659","tid":178409,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠做左十幾廿年D POINT都係咁ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caba1435cf4cc05ac2b28b91dca737ff659b3d92","tid":178409,"uid":8426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"根本係公屋既入息上限戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014d8cf7dff6a03e34818801c2586bd2740c982f","tid":178409,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"5蚊一個鐘好冇，乜撚公屋低津都申請到呀屌你老母廿蚊張"},{"pid":"368a7a1348b044ef29ad424a7e3ffba7f78b97db","tid":178409,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"多謝廿蚊張再煲慶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04827efd2a2f8c3d8d9f70208080a27e50a5db85","tid":178409,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"反正都唔會排到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6aa599153b283cb4535d79b7ab7dc4ccff1abc","tid":178409,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"洗碗的確17k 不過12碼<br />\n唔撚係人做"},{"pid":"3bad1a6149a8ff403a47b7c48dc1f2fff4d5ebc0","tid":178409,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}